text_raw:
2. The 1st day of May 2020 is appointed as the day on which Part 3 of the 
Criminal Justice (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 2009 (No. 28 of 2009) shall 
come into operation. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Minister for Justice 
and Equality, 

28 April, 2020. 

CHARLES FLANAGAN, 

Minister for Justice and Equality. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 1st May, 2020.
